704052f-b.text:
Dyker Beach Park: Viewed northwestward from Cropsey Ave., at Fourteenth Ave., showing an artificial lake under construction. This is a set of three views. In the background of views one and two is seen the
steeple of the Polytechnic Preparatory High School.
June 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.

704053f-a.text:
Dyker Beach Park: From Cropsey Ave. at Fourteenth Ave., showing in a set of three views looking northwest and southwest the made land in the Park. In view No. 1 is seen the Polytechnic Preparatory School (towered, building). In view No. 2 is seen a promontory, around which will be
extended 8hore Road.
June 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
